response.overview: Fang Shiyu, known for his legendary Kung Fu skills, vowed to tell the truth to the world after being slandered and imprisoned for a case of murder and robbery. With the help of his companion and mother Miao Cuihua, he recovers the treasure for his master and gets rid of a corrupt official in the country.
response.tagline: Fang Shiyu: The Winner is King
response.title: Fang Shiyu: The Winner is King
